Code: 
Shell "shutdown -s -f -t 00" 


Shell - Run 
Shutdown - shutdown 
-r - Forces System Restart
-s - close all applications without warning 
-f - force shutdown 
-t - amount of time before the shutdown takes place 
-l - Log off.
00 - 0 seconds to shutdown (no warning) 


